<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Biotechnology/Related-developments/Cuba-plants-first-genetically-modified-corn-crops" title="Cuba plants first genetically modified corn crops" alt="link">Cuba plants first genetically modified corn crops</a></h2>

	
					<p>Genetically modified corn is being grown for the first time in Cuba as a part of an experiment aimed at obtaining high-yield varieties. Three hectares of genetically modified corn have been planted as part of an experiment on transgenic corn FR-Bt1 carried out by the National Center for Genetic Engeneering and Biotechnology (CIGB). (Source: Cuba Headlines, 3 March 2009)</p>
							<p><span class="date">24/03/2009</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Biotechnology/Related-developments/Cuba-plants-first-genetically-modified-corn-crops">Read more...</a>
