						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Biotechnology/Related-developments/Urgent-call-for-global-fight-against-wheat-killer" title="Urgent call for global fight against wheat killer" alt="link">Urgent call for global fight against wheat killer</a></h2>

	
					<p>Representatives of major wheat producing countries have called for urgent coordinated action to prevent and control the wheat stem rust disease strain Ug99. Affected countries and countries at risk should develop contingency plans to prevent rust epidemics that could result in devastating yield losses. Plant breeding research should be intensified and international cooperation enhanced to develop new Ug99 resistant varieties (Source: FAO, 12 November 2008). </p>
